skill.name: Fists of Thunder
skill.description:
Generate: 6 Spirit per attack

Unleash a series of extremely fast punches that deal 110% weapon damage as Lightning. Every third hit deals damage to all enemies in front of you and knocks them back a short distance. Generates Spirit faster than other Spirit-generating skills due to the high attack speed.
skill.simpleDescription:
Generate: 6 Spirit per attack

Attack a single target with a series of rapid punches that can knockback enemies.

rune.name: Lightning Flash
rune.description: Increases your chance to Dodge by 16% for 2 seconds.

skill.name: Cyclone Strike
skill.description:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Pull all enemies within 24 yards towards you, followed by a furious blast of energy that deals 100% weapon damage as Holy.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Mystical force pulls nearby enemies towards you and blasts them.

rune.name: Wall of Wind
rune.description: After using Cyclone Strike, gain a 20% chance to dodge attacks for 3 seconds.
rune.simpleDescription: After using Cyclone Strike, gain a chance to dodge attacks for a limited time.

skill.name: Sweeping Wind
skill.description:
Cost: 75 Spirit

Surround yourself in a vortex that continuously deals 15% weapon damage to all enemies within 10 yards. The vortex lasts 6 seconds and is refreshed each time you strike an enemy with a melee attack. Landing a Critical Hit has a chance to increase the vortex effect up to 2 times for a total of 45% weapon damage to nearby enemies.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 75 Spirit

Surround yourself in a vortex that damages nearby enemies. Critical Hits intensify the vortex.

rune.name: Cyclone
rune.description: While your vortex is at the maximum stack count, Critical Hits have a chance to spawn a lightning tornado that periodically electrocutes nearby enemies for 20% weapon damage as Lightning. Each spawned lightning tornado lasts 3 seconds.
rune.simpleDescription: While the vortex is at its maximum, every Critical Hit spawns a lightning tornado that electrocutes enemies.

skill.name: Serenity
skill.description:
Cost: 10 Spirit
Cooldown: 20 seconds

You are enveloped in a protective shield that absorbs all incoming damage for 3 seconds and grants immunity to all control impairing effects.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 10 Spirit
Cooldown: 20 seconds

Become immune to all attacks and control effects for 3 seconds.

rune.name: Peaceful Repose
rune.description: When activated, Serenity heals you for 6202 - 7752 Life.

skill.name: Seven-Sided Strike
skill.description:
Cost: 50 Spirit
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Dash rapidly between nearby enemies, dealing 1777% weapon damage over 7 hits.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 50 Spirit
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Move with blinding speed and strike nearby enemies while being immune to attacks yourself.

rune.name: Fulminating Onslaught
rune.description: Each strike explodes, dealing 254% weapon damage as Holy in a 7 yard radius around the target.
rune.simpleDescription: Each strike triggers an explosion that deals Holy damage.

skill.name: Mantra of Evasion
skill.description:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Recite a Mantra that grants you and your allies within 40 yards a 15% chance to dodge attacks for 3 minutes.

For 3 seconds after activation, a second effect grants an additional 15% chance to dodge attacks.

This is a Mantra. You can only have one Mantra active at a time.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Increase your and your allies' chance to dodge attacks.

Only one Mantra can be active at a time.

rune.name: Backlash
rune.description: Successfully dodging an attack has a chance to create a burst of flame dealing 35% weapon damage as Fire to all nearby enemies.
rune.simpleDescription: Successfully dodging an attack has a chance to create a burst of flame that damages nearby enemies.

skill.name: Sixth Sense
skill.description: Your dodge chance is increased by an amount equal to 30% of your Critical Hit Chance.
skill.flavor: The final test of the Serpent's Form takes place in "The Pit of 12 Vipers." The initiates are not told about the 13th.

skill.name: Transcendence
skill.description: Every point of Spirit spent heals you for 62.0 Life.
skill.flavor: A life unlived is no different than death.

skill.name: Seize the Initiative
skill.description: Your Armor is increased by 100% of your Dexterity.
skill.flavor: The Monks of Ivgorod are trained to move like waterâ€”flowing freely into open spaces and crashing hard against their foes.

skill.name: Intimidate
skill.description: Enemy units are slowed by 60% for 3 seconds when they hit the Templar.
skill.simpleDescription: Enemies attacking the Templar are slowed.

skill.name: Onslaught
skill.description:
Delivers a massive blow to an enemy for 200% weapon damage.

Cooldown: 15 seconds
skill.simpleDescription: Delivers a massive blow to an enemy.

skill.name: Inspire
skill.description:
Increase resource generation for all allies that the Templar is following.
Mana: 2 per second.
Arcane Power: 0.5 per second.
Hatred: 1 per second.
Fury: 8% generated.
Spirit: 12% generated.

skill.name: Crippling Shot
skill.description:
Ranged attack that slows the target by 60% for 3 seconds.

Cooldown: 6 seconds
skill.simpleDescription: Deals damage and slows the target.

skill.name: Dirty Fighting
skill.description:
Blinds enemies in front of the Scoundrel for 3 seconds.

Cooldown: 30 seconds

skill.name: Powered Shot
skill.description:
Powerful ranged attack that explodes on impact, dealing 25% weapon damage as Arcane to targets within 6 yards and has a 50% chance to Stun targets for 2 seconds.

Cooldown: 20 seconds
skill.simpleDescription: Deals massive damage in an area and knocks back enemies.

skill.name: Anatomy
skill.description: Increases Critical Hit Chance by 3% for the Scoundrel and his allies.
skill.simpleDescription: Increases the Critical Hit Chance of the Scoundrel and his allies.

mainHand.name: Severe High Priest Staff of Immolation

skill.name: Forceful Push
skill.description:
Summon an Arcane explosion 8 yards around an enemy, dealing 100% weapon damage as Arcane and knocking back all monsters caught within it.

Cooldown: 10 seconds
skill.simpleDescription: Creates an explosion that deals massive damage and knocks back enemies.

skill.name: Reflect Missiles
skill.description:
Place a shield on the Enchantress and her allies that reflects incoming projectiles for 5 seconds.

Cooldown: 20 seconds
skill.simpleDescription: Creates a shield around the Enchantress and her allies that reflects projectiles.

skill.name: Erosion
skill.description:
Conjures a pool of energy that deals 50% weapon damage as Arcane per second. Affected enemies take an extra 15% damage from all attacks for 3 seconds.

Cooldown: 15 seconds
skill.simpleDescription: Blasts a target area, causing enemies to take damage over time.

skill.name: Focused Mind
skill.description: An aura that increases attack speed by 3% for allies within 40 yards.
skill.simpleDescription: Increases the attack speed of the Enchantress and her allies.
